public abstract class Function2DList
extends java.lang.Object
implements XYDataset, NamedObjectAPI

Title: Function2DList
Description: List container for 2D Functions. Subclasses deal with particular types of 2D Functions.

Implement XYDataSet so that it can be passed into the JRefinery Graphing Package
